<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Demande d'aide mentor — AllAboard</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#0f172a;font-family:'Inter',Arial,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#0f172a;padding:40px 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#1e293b;border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">

          <%# Header %>
          <tr>
            <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#6366f1);padding:36px 40px;text-align:center;">
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:14px;padding:12px 16px;">
                    <span style="font-size:24px;">🎓</span>
                    <span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;margin-left:8px;vertical-align:middle;">AllAboard</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <%# Body %>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:40px 40px 32px;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 6px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:14px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">Demande d'aide</p>
              <h1 style="margin:0 0 8px;color:#ffffff;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;">
                🆘 Un étudiant a besoin de toi !
              </h1>
              <p style="margin:0 0 24px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:15px;">
                Bonjour <strong style="color:#e2e8f0;"><%= @mentor.display_name %></strong>,
                <strong style="color:#e2e8f0;"><%= @author.display_name %></strong> a besoin d'aide sur un sujet qui correspond à tes compétences.
              </p>

              <%# Matière badge %>
              <div style="margin-bottom:16px;">
                <span style="display:inline-block;background:rgba(16,185,129,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.3);color:#10b981;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:999px;">
                  <%= @post.subject.name %>
                </span>
              </div>

              <%# Post %>
              <div style="background:rgba(16,185,129,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.2);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:28px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 8px;color:#64748b;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">Post de <%= @author.display_name %></p>
                <p style="margin:0 0 10px;color:#f1f5f9;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;"><%= @post.title %></p>
                <p style="margin:0;color:#94a3b8;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;"><%= @post.body.truncate(200) %></p>
              </div>

              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding:0 0 28px;">
                    <%= link_to post_url(@post),
                                style: "display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#6366f1);color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;padding:14px 36px;border-radius:14px;" do %>
                      Voir le post et aider
                    <% end %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:0;color:#475569;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;">
                Tu reçois cet e-mail car tu es mentor sur AllAboard et tes compétences correspondent à cette demande.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <%# Footer %>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px 40px 32px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
              <p style="margin:0;color:#334155;font-size:12px;text-align:center;">
                © <%= Date.current.year %> AllAboard — La plateforme d'entraide étudiante<br>
                Cet e-mail a été envoyé à <strong style="color:#475569;"><%= @mentor.email %></strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
